---
title: Sirloin and Tangy Steak Sauce with Crispy Green Beans and Rosemary Potatoes
description: Le menu: Seared sirloin drizzled with savory pan glaze. Roasted rosemary-scented potatoes. Buttery green beans topped with garlicky toasted bread crumbs. Your upcoming restaurant reservation: cancel that!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/2018w52r16c-steakhouse-sirloin-87eb08b9.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/2018w52r16c-steakhouse-sirloin-5be44d9aae08b568a34cb8a2-656f4ca8.pdf
